redux ek global store hai for example mere pass ek parent component hai usme mene koi api hit krle or mere pass kiya agaya data agaya uske baad us parent component k teen ya char child ha mujhe agr usme data pass krna hoga to kese pass kro ga props sai data pass kro ga phir uske child ma data pass krna hoga to usme bhi props sai he pass kro ga ye kiya ha pure hirerachy chal rahe ha hierarchy mai sai sub sai upar sai data a raha ha 
parent sai phele ek k props ma gaya usko chor kr dosre k props ma gaya to kiya hota ja raha thora complex hota ja raha hai or koi aesa component ha jo mere hirerachy mai mujood nhi hai phir global store banae ga wo har component ko access hoga chaiye wo hierarchy mai ho ya na ho  
component--->action--->reducer--->store--->component
component mai sai koi ek aesa function call krte ha jo return ma hum kuch na kuch provide kr raha hota hai action k kaam hai k wo reducer tak data lekr jae or store ko update kre phir component mai uske props sai hume naya data mile ga 
store.dispatch method jo action k kaam krta ha k wo reducer ma ja kr condition check kre ga agr condition true hojae ge to wahi ruk jae ga
reducer koi piece of state provide kr raha hota ya phir usko manage kr raha hota 
